{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "茶馆小二",
  "entry": "n_1",
  "meta": {
    "title": "茶馆·小二"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "got_iron_box",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "after_box_1"
        },
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "waiter_met",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "return_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "first_1"
    },
    "first_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "哟，关二狗，今天又来蹭茶气迈？先说好，赊起那两碗茶钱老子可记得清楚的。",
      "next": "first_set_met",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "first_set_met": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "waiter_met",
            "value": true
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "first_choice"
    },
    "first_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a",
          "text": "少啰嗦，瞎子李今天啷个来了",
          "next": "first_a"
        },
        {
          "id": "b",
          "text": "张叨叨今天讲啥子",
          "next": "first_b"
        }
      ]
    },
    "first_a": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "刚摸进来没好久。你要真有事求他，先等张叨叨把那段书摆完嘛，免得那老瞎子嫌你毛焦火辣。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "first_b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "还不是那些神仙道士、坟里头爬出来的怪东西。可偏偏茶客就爱听勒个。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "return_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "又来咯？今天这茶馆可没得啥子空位，想听书就自己挤一哈。",
      "next": "return_choice",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "return_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "r1",
          "text": "瞎子李好说话吗",
          "next": "return_r1"
        },
        {
          "id": "r2",
          "text": "城隍庙那点最近闹啥子怪",
          "next": "return_r2"
        },
        {
          "id": "r3",
          "text": "没得啥事，我随便转哈",
          "next": "return_r3"
        }
      ]
    },
    "return_r1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "next": "end1",
      "text": "哪个晓得葛，那老瞎子看着和气，真要不顺心，嘴巴比刀子还快。你自己掂量着点说哈。",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "return_r2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "next": "return_r2b",
      "text": "你还真问着了。前几天有人翻出一张旧戏单，说当年柳家班就在城隍庙戏台唱过堂会，后来班里那个最红的旦角，说没落就没落了。",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "return_r2b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "next": "return_r2flags",
      "text": "这几天城里又有人说，夜里头从庙后头过，能听见女人吊起嗓子唱戏。有人说她是在害人，也有人说她像是在找人。",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "return_r2flags": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "heard_waiter_ghost_talk",
            "value": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "heard_opera_rumor",
            "value": true
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "return_r3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "next": "end1",
      "text": "转嘛转嘛，莫碰翻茶碗就要得。",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "after_box_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "next": "after_choice",
      "text": "咦，你啷个一副魂都掉了的样子？刚才不是还在瞎子李那点赔笑脸迈。",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "after_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "x",
          "text": "没得啥事，先切了",
          "next": "after_x"
        },
        {
          "id": "y",
          "text": "给老子倒碗凉茶压一哈惊",
          "next": "after_y"
        }
      ]
    },
    "after_x": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "next": "end1",
      "text": "要得，走路看到点，莫又把自己摔沟里头切了。",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "after_y": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "next": "end1",
      "text": "稀奇，关二狗也有肯掏钱喝茶的时候迈？算了，这碗先记到账上。",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    },
    "n_1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a",
          "text": "选项甲",
          "next": "root"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "preconditions": []
}
